text: Justyna Iskrzycka (born 7 November 1997) is a Polish sprint canoeist. She participated at the 2018 ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships, winning a medal.K-2 1000 m results ==References== Category:Living people Category:1997 births Category:Polish female canoeists Category:ICF Canoe Sprint World Championships medalists in kayak Category:European Games competitors for Poland Category:Canoeists at the 2019 European Games Category:Sportspeople from Bielsko-Biała
